question: 1 (i)
statement_html: Find the volume of the solid of revolution generated by revolving about the x-axis the region under the graph \(\displaystyle y = x^{3/2}\) from \(\displaystyle x=0\) to \(\displaystyle x=2\).
statement_latex:
Find the volume of the solid of revolution generated by revolving about
the \emph{x}-axis the region under the graph $\displaystyle y = x^{3/2}$
from $\displaystyle x=0$ to $\displaystyle x=2$.
statement_raw: Find the volume of the solid of revolution generated by revolving about the ''x''-axis the region under the graph <math> \displaystyle y = x^{3/2}</math> from <math> \displaystyle x=0</math> to <math> \displaystyle x=2</math>.
